at could make that a reality.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Jan 2023) 0aDetention of personszGreat Britain. 0aPolice powerzGreat Britain. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Criminology.2bisacsh1 aSanders, Andrew, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2018z978311119666440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781447343684423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781447343684/original  a978-3-11-119666-4  Bristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2018b2018  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK